1
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:16,440
The deputy mayor of the city is retiring these days.

2
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,570
The competition for

3
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:19,120
this position is fierce.

4
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:21,170
With your abilities and level,

5
00:01:21,240 --> 00:01:22,360
the new deputy mayor

6
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,280
has to be you.

7
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:24,780
Abilities?

8
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:26,000
We have a female division head

9
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,760
who hasn't been working long.

10
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:29,520
She has strong connections.

11
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:31,520
The former division head was just 50

12
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,660
and got pushed out.

13
00:01:33,759 --> 00:01:34,820
Do you need my help?

14
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:37,280
You know,

15
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:41,000
I hate collusion between officials and businessmen the most.

16
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,240
Old classmate,

17
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:43,440
I'm helping you

18
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:45,440
and I don't need anything in return.

19
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:47,970
This isn't about getting anything in return.

20
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,600
It's unfair to others.

21
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,920
We've all experienced too much unfairness.

22
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,479
I hope the unfairness in this society

23
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:55,039
can be reduced as much as possible.

24
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,479
It's exactly for fairness

25
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:57,080
that we need

26
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:59,009
leading cadres like you to step up.

27
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,360
Seize this opportunity,

28
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:03,800
okay?

29
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,180
Qiming.

30
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:07,440
Are you...

31
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:10,280
Hello.

32
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,720
The bank loan needs your signature.

33
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,780
Come over quickly.

34
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,640
Okay, I'll be right there.

35
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,410
Go ahead if you're busy.

36
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,340
Old classmate.

37
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:21,840
Trust me.

38
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:26,760
I do.

39
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:35,800
It's time.

40
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,000
Look at these photos.

41
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,040
Not bad.

42
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,450
I'll give you another 50,000 yuan.

43
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:54,920
Don't tell anyone about this.

44
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,900
Do you understand?

45
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,680
Understood.

46
00:02:59,040 --> 00:02:59,600
Go.

47
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:25,120
This bidding proposal is fake.

48
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,600
You've been set up.

49
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,500
I really underestimated him.

50
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,180
It's a pity about the project.

51
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,640
He's already suspicious of you.

52
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,960
I guess you won't be staying long.

53
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,500
He won't be able to kick me out.

54
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,460
After all, we are in the same boat.

55
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:55,880
Unless he wants mutual destruction.

56
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,900
Doesn't he still have that precious son?

57
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,980
Qiming is here.

58
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:15,890
Your calligraphy is getting better and better, sir.

59
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,040
Qiming.

60
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,560
I heard from Jiang Tao

61
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:22,690
that your company is doing a project in the western suburbs.

62
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:23,520
Yes.

63
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,320
We encountered some difficulties.

64
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,850
It's not about the project.

65
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,700
It's about fair competition.

66
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,370
So what do you think?

67
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,650
I want to change all of this.

68
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,840
I'm ready.

69
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,530
Inappropriate.

70
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,040
Your idea is very dangerous.

71
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,120
I'm not doing it for myself.

72
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,120
I won't regret it.

73
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:45,720
Qiming.

74
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:50,440
Don't be too stubborn.

75
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,880
Listen to me.

76
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:57,440
Qiming,

77
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,970
I will give you a piece of calligraphy.

78
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,180
Thank you, sir.

79
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:08,280
Great virtue carries all things.

80
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,700
Thank you so much, sir.

81
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,450
I won't bother you anymore.

82
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,860
Thank you, sir.

83
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,360
Qiming, wait for me.

84
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,200
Slow down.

85
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,120
This is the company. What are you doing?

86
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:34,120
Ye Qiming, I don't care if it's the company!

87
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:34,960
Ye Qiming!

88
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,880
Yu Na.

89
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,409
What did you call me?

90
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:43,800
Yu Na.

91
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,880
Suspend all your current projects.

92
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:48,850
Take paid leave.

93
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,200
I was the one following up on the projects.

94
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,000
Why stop them just because you say so?

95
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,080
Calm down.

96
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,360
If you keep acting like this,

97
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,450
just go home now.

98
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,900
I have sacrificed so much.

99
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,780
I must get everything.

100
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,360
Rest assured.

101
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:26,040
Ye Yuan will definitely become

102
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,480
the most powerful tool against Ye Qiming.

103
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,600
Little guy.

104
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,680
How have you been lately?

105
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,280
I'm doing okay.

106
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:10,730
Let's go.

107
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:11,850
Okay.

108
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,540
Let me carry it for you.

109
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:21,620
Hello, sir.

110
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:23,010
Please show your ID.

111
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,560
Thank you for your cooperation.

112
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,210
Open the trunk, please.

113
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,060
You are the fresh blood of our bureau,

114
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,080
and you are very capable.

115
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:56,960
But

116
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,560
Tian Liang's case

117
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,240
and Lu Yang's case

118
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,820
have made no progress,

119
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,980
causing an uproar in the city.

120
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,770
Now the higher authorities

121
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,300
are very dissatisfied

122
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,360
with our work.

123
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,520
Chief Wu.

124
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,120
Shen Feng and I have been investigating.

125
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,600
I...

126
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,250
I don't care about the process.

127
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:19,540
If it's murder,

128
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,200
there must be a killer.

129
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,130
If it's suicide,

130
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,820
there must be a reason.

131
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:25,800
Yes.

132
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,960
Having pressure

133
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:30,080
isn't a bad thing.

134
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,320
Treat it as an experience.

135
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,000
Turn the pressure

136
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:36,920
into motivation.

137
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,520
I understand.

138
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,320
But we won't shirk our responsibilities.

139
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,160
There is indeed a problem on our end.

140
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:44,920
This case

141
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,520
has dragged on for too long.

142
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,600
Use your initiative.

143
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:52,080
Don't doubt your abilities.

144
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:54,210
I believe in you.

145
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:55,970
You can do it.

146
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,760
We will definitely do our best

147
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:58,360
and strive

148
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,860
to solve the case soon.

149
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,170
What a coincidence.

150
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,120
What's wrong? You look down.

151
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,360
You must be getting pressure from above.

152
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:17,160
The chief and the others are probably anxious too.

153
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,810
Aren't you anxious?

154
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:21,560
The longer it drags on, the worse it is for the case.

155
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,690
Don't you know that?

156
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,000
Open a new line of inquiry

157
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,490
and investigate Ye Qiming.

158
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,740
How do you open this candy?

159
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,240
How could there be a traffic accident?

160
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:34,970
Look into it.

161
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,840
Find out what exactly happened.

162
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:39,000
Just invite him to the police station

163
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,320
under the pretext of the migrant worker accident.

164
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:41,760
Okay.

165
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:44,020
We can use this chance to warn him.

166
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:47,960
Mr. Ye.

167
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,920
We asked you to come here today

168
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:54,080
to find out a few things.

169
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,480
Some time ago,

170
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:58,480
I heard you owed the village demolition compensation,

171
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,840
and the villagers got into a car accident on their way to collect the debt.

172
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,960
To show your apology,

173
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,280
you delivered the money to them in person.

174
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:04,080
Is that right?

175
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:04,880
Yes.

176
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,640
Our company let the villagers down.

177
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,120
We shouldn't have owed them money.

178
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,600
The responsibility is mine.

179
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,400
It's good that you realize that.

180
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:14,210
Regarding the demolition,

181
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,210
did you go to the village often?

182
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:16,600
Yes.

183
00:11:16,880 --> 00:11:17,560
For work,

184
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,240
I went there frequently.

185
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:19,960
By the way,

186
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,840
regarding this traffic accident,

187
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,800
please rest assured,

188
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:24,040
and tell the villagers to rest assured too.

189
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,880
We will investigate it jointly with the traffic police brigade

190
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:28,480
and definitely find the vehicle responsible.

191
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,440
I thank you both on behalf of the villagers.

192
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,520
Thank you for your cooperation too, Mr. Ye.

193
00:11:33,520 --> 00:11:35,360
Cooperating with the investigation is our responsibility and duty.

194
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:35,840
Yes.

195
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,080
Then there's another matter

196
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,600
we need your cooperation on.

197
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,130
Go ahead.

198
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,500
Regarding Lu Yang,

199
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,180
we are also very sorry.

200
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:44,600
Yes.

201
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,580
I sponsored Lu Yang's education.

202
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:51,240
I didn't expect such an accident to happen.

203
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,680
Besides your annual sponsorship,

204
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:56,040
did any other organization or individual sponsor him?

205
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,370
I don't know about that.

206
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:59,800
But there's one thing I find puzzling.

207
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:00,960
I heard from Huang Xiaoyun

208
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:02,840
that he often went to places like bars,

209
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,040
drinking and stuff,

210
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,580
and spent money lavishly.

211
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,600
I think

212
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,700
he shouldn't have been like that.

213
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:09,840
Could you tell us your impression

214
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,680
of Lu Yang?

215
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,360
I had very little contact with him,

216
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,480
so I don't know him well.

217
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,080
Then why did you sponsor him?

218
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:18,680
Mainly because we are from the same hometown.

219
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:20,280
We are from the same village.

220
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:23,600
It's not easy for someone from our place to get into college.

221
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:26,200
I didn't want him to go through the hardships

222
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,300
that I experienced back then.

223
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,500
So I sponsored him,

224
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,130
so he could focus on school,

225
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:33,580
and contribute to society in the future.

226
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,560
Given your relationship with Huang Xiaoyun,

227
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:37,520
we'd like to ask,

228
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,680
about their relationship.

229
00:12:39,680 --> 00:12:40,940
What do you think of it?

230
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,720
That's their own business.

231
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,080
I don't care.

232
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,760
Didn't Huang Xiaoyun ask for your opinion?

233
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:49,280
I'm busy from morning till night every day.

234
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:52,320
I basically have no personal communication with her.

235
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:52,800
None.

236
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:54,440
So did you know or not?

237
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:57,400
I guess I knew a little.

238
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,680
How did you know?

239
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:02,080
Does this have anything to do with the case?

240
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:04,040
No.

241
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,600
I just want to understand

242
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,660
Xiaoyun and Lu Yang's relationship.

243
00:13:09,160 --> 00:13:10,160
Then I'm sorry.

244
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:12,660
If you want to know,

245
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:13,920
you can ask my wife Xia Lin.

246
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:15,720
She knows much more than I do.

247
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:18,920
I see.

248
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:23,840
Did you go near Lu Yang's house the day he had the accident?

249
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,600
Yes.

250
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:27,200
I went to talk to the villagers about development.

251
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,530
Did you see Lu Yang then?

252
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,490
No, I didn't.

253
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:33,120
So you went straight home after work that day?

254
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,960
That night,

255
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:36,770
I got home around 10:20.

256
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,260
What's the matter?

257
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:40,080
You truly are a businessman, Mr. Ye.

258
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:40,440
Yes,

259
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,460
remembering the time so clearly.

260
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:43,600
After 9:00 that night,

261
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,800
I also called Lu Yang.

262
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:46,680
I told him to study hard.

263
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:48,420
I didn't expect

264
00:13:49,160 --> 00:13:50,690
it to be our last phone call.

265
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:54,000
You've done all you could.

266
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:55,930
My condolences.

267
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,520
Thank you. Thank you.

268
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,320
Officers,

269
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:01,210
is there anything else?

270
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,740
If not, I'll take my leave.

271
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:05,240
Of course.

272
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,640
Thank you for your cooperation.

273
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:07,120
Okay.

274
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,920
Thank you. Thank you.

275
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,000
Do you need us to see you out?

276
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,200
No need, please stay.

277
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:12,840
Goodbye.

278
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,400
Thank you.

279
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:13,930
Goodbye.

280
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:20,480
Watertight.

281
00:14:21,920 --> 00:14:23,980
He's been in business for a long time,

282
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,760
so he won't tell you anything easily

283
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:29,170
unless you have leverage over him.

284
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:32,640
But judging from the shoe prints and tire tracks,

285
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,160
he did go to Lu Yang's house

286
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,200
and observed him.

287
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:38,040
He admitted going near Lu Yang's house,

288
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:40,610
but there are no footprints of his inside,

289
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:43,140
nor are there any fingerprints on the stove.

290
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:45,250
Did Lu Yang turn on the gas himself?

291
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:46,960
Theoretically, yes.

292
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,700
But he came all this way just to take a look at Lu Yang?

293
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:52,320
Lu Yang's death.

294
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,800
No clues for homicide.

295
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,060
No motive for suicide.

296
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,000
It's too strange.

297
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:05,000
Isn't this Mr. Shen?

298
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:07,560
Are your old arms and legs still doing okay?

299
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:08,160
So-so.

300
00:15:10,400 --> 00:15:10,960
No way.

301
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,360
Let me ask you something.

302
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:14,920
Why did you retire from the frontline back then?

303
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:16,180
If you hadn't retired,

304
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,600
I'd have to call you Captain now.

305
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:19,480
Please don't.

306
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:22,080
You leaders love to joke around.

307
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:23,880
Forget it if you won't say.

308
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:24,480
Come here.

309
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:31,160
Tell me.

310
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:36,240
There are many colleagues around. Don't make me look like I'm flaunting my seniority.

311
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,040
You are still

312
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:38,480
young now.

313
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,800
When you reach 30, you'll feel

314
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,560
a 9-to-5 job is okay.

315
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:45,320
I don't feel that way.

316
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,280
You can't feel it.

317
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,920
You'll hope you never do.

318
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,600
As for you.

319
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:49,880
Want some coffee?

320
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:51,440
I'll make you a cup.

321
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,240
Captain Shen.

322
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:53,640
Want some coffee?

323
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:54,560
Sure.

324
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:55,530
Two cups.

325
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:56,840
What is it?

326
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,210
Your letter.

327
00:15:58,560 --> 00:15:59,160
My letter?

328
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,680
Don't let your mentor make coffee.

329
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:02,410
I'll make it.

330
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,120
What's wrong?

331
00:16:11,120 --> 00:16:11,650
Nothing.

332
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:15,400
Captain Shen.
